  "title": "Customer Service Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Work Location: 232 Pandan Loop</strong></p><p><strong>5.5 days workweek, </strong><br /><strong>Mon to Friday 10 am to 7 pm.</strong><br /><strong>Sat OFF, </strong><br /><strong>Sunday 3 pm to 7 pm (WFH)</strong><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Reports to the Customer Service Manager</li><li>Responding promptly to customer inquiries</li><li>Processing and coordinating customers’ orders, forms, applications, and requests</li><li>Ensure customer satisfaction and provide professional customer support</li><li>Communicating with customers through various channels</li><li>Communicating and coordinating with various internal staff and stakeholders as necessary pertaining to customers’ orders, enquiries etc</li><li>Good understanding and knowledge of company’s products</li><li>Generates and processes new sales leads as necessary</li><li>Update of product item code in the company’s system and expiry date management of products</li><li>Compile and generate various monthly reports for the sales team</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 years of related experience preferably with food & beverage exposure</li><li>Positive attitude and customer service minded</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Excel, Words)</li><li>Good communication and negotiation skills</li><li>Proactive in solving problems</li><li>Passionate, highly driven, independent, able to work under pressure and as well as multi-tasking</li></ul>",
